{"tid":655322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人成日話自己嘅母語係廣東話，我唔認同。","createTime":"2018-05-06T11:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T13:46:50.000Z","uid":138177,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e5d0c4cc65a4e958e507beaa526f283250d6d9","tid":655322,"uid":138177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"俾我會話係香港話囉好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然話就話唔少香港人（包括小弟）嘅祖父母輩親戚都係廣東人<br />\n但係呢度係香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係廣東！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n況且香港話（港式粵語）同廣東話、廣府話、潮州話本來就有好明顯分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再者點解潮州可以有潮州話<br />\n香港就唔可以有香港話？<br />\n<br />\n我會咁唸，<br />\n香港人嘅母語係香港話！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁鐘意叫「廣東」話唔該返廣東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：小弟本人同父母喺香港出世長大、全家無人有外國護照同BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、全家都講香港話"},{"pid":"474427d8e76b4aae82a9de8c97bf80827df7aa5e","tid":655322,"uid":6195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T12:20:46.000Z","msg":"你兩老97前拎咩護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定淨係識返大陸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86de381628ad9f755e012e982d1e29fb4d101959","tid":655322,"uid":138177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"474427d8e76b4aae82a9de8c97bf80827df7aa5e","tid":655322,"uid":6195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T12:20:46.000Z","msg":"你兩老97前拎咩護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定淨係識返大陸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"我估係BNO（家母講過佢97前去過新加坡Field trip）<br />\n不過無續期咁解<br />\n<br />\n再者<br />\n我兩老本來就唔鐘意離港<img src=\"/assets